<p>The mark disappears when the checkbox is clicked.  The mark will be green when
the checkbox is already set.</p>

<div>
  <label for="cb_read" class="form-label">Licenses:</label>
  <div class="form-check" data-added-in="20251010">
    <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="read" value="read" id="cb_read" required>
    <label class="form-check-label" for="rb_read">Please confirm you read the conditions.</label>
  </div>
</div>
